HEADWORD: Exceptive
<hw>Ex*cept"ive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>That excepts;
including an exception; <as>as, an <ex>exceptive</ex>
proposition</as>.</def> <rj><au>I. Watts.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A particular and <qex>exceptive</qex> law.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Exceptless</ent>⟦br⟧
